# AI Lint Prompt Experiment

`import '<root>/.ai`

## Outupt
* Generate a new file with the same name, but with `.txt` extension rather than `.tsx`

##  Rule Format
* **[Rule Type]** *Text of Prompt*

###  Rules
* **`[Imports]`** Each file in `src/server` never imports anything from `src/client`
* **`[ImportAlias]`** All imports use `@app/` import aliases
* **`[SortImports]`** Imports are sorted according to length
* **`[FileRules]`** Each file should export the enum without using default
* **`[VariableNaming]`** Each enum value should have a `Type` suffix for instance `enum MyEnumType`
* **`[RepoStructure]`** each directory in the repo is lowercase under `src`
* **`[RepoStructure]`** File under `src` starts with an uppercase for `.tsx` files
